name: ASTRAL SWIM /// GENESIS collectible poem edition
description:
Like a diamond, 
I am,
Pressure,
Refined,
Coal in my soul,
Into an indestructible shine.

Rare,
I am,
One of a kind,
Bare,
Sparkling mind,
Formed over time,
Surviving,
Rising,
Thriving,
Every moment,
Is my genesis.
